newsitem.title: GERMANY: SOCCER-BORUSSIA DORTMUND V ATLETICO MADRID TEAMS.
newsitem.headline: SOCCER-BORUSSIA DORTMUND V ATLETICO MADRID TEAMS.

text.p: Teams for Wednesday's European Champions' League group B match between Borussia Dortmund of Germany and Atletico Madrid of Spain:

Borussia Dortmund - 1-Stefan Klos, 7-Stefan Reuter, 25-Steinar Pedersen, 5-Julio Cesar, 23-Rene Tretschok, 14-Paul Lambert, 10-Andreas Moeller, 8-Michael Zorc, 2-Knut Reinhardt, 11-Heiko Herrlich, 9-Stephane Chapuisat
Atletico Madrid - 1-Jose Francisco Molina, 20-Delfi Geli, 6-Santi, 4-Roberto Solozabal, 3-Toni, 18-Roberto, 24-Radek Bejbl, 10-Milinko Pantic, 8-Juan Vizcaino, 9-Juan Esnaider, 19-Kiko
